ued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"William Gremislaw was born in 1314, in Scotland, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 daughter with Margaret Brunston. He died in 1393, in his hometown, at the age of 79."},"et":{"1314–1393":"1314–1393","1325–1410":"1325–1410","1356–1429":"1356–1429","1314":"1314","1325":"1325","1356":"1356","1410":"1410","1393":"1393","1429":"1429","Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland":"Edinburgh, Scotland","Scotland":"Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1314–1393":"1314–1393","1325–1410":"1325–1410","1356–1429":"1356–1429","1314":"1314","1325":"1325","1356":"1356","1410":"1410","1393":"1393","1429":"1429","Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland":"Edinburgh, Scotland","Scotland":"Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1314–1393":"1314–1393","1325–1410":"1325–1410","1356–1429":"1356–1429","1314":"1314","1325":"1325","1356":"1356","1410":"1410","1393":"1393","1429":"1429","Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland":"Edinburgh, Écosse","Scotland":"Écosse, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"William Gremislaw est né en 1314, à Écosse, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fille avec Margaret Brunston. Il est décédé en 1393, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 79 ans."},"de":{"1314–1393":"1314–1393","1325–1410":"1325–1410","1356–1429":"1356–1429","1314":"1314","1325":"1325","1356":"1356","1410":"1410","1393":"1393","1429":"1429","Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland":"Edinburgh, Scotland","Scotland":"Schottland, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"William Gremislaw wurde 1314 in Schottland, United Kingdom geboren. Er hatte mit Margaret Brunston mindestens 1 Tochter. Er starb 1393 im Alter von 79 Jahren in seinem Geburtsort."},"ht":{"1314–1393":"1314–1393","1325–1410":"1325–1410","1356–1429":"1356–1429","1314":"1314","1325":"1325","1356":"1356","1410":"1410","1393":"1393","1429":"1429","Edinburgh, Midlothian, Scotland":"Edinburgh, Scotland","Scotland":"Ecosse, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"1314–1393":"1314–1393","